Package io.github.dranreb22

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioPlayer
    Class AudioPlayer extends Product and is meant to serve as a type of product to be created based on ItemTypes chosen.
    Main
    Default main class starts the GUI.
    MoviePlayer
    Class MoviePlayer extends Product and implements MultimediaControl; meant to serve as a type of product to be created based on ItemTypes chosen.
    Product
    Abstract class Product implementing Item interface and being extended by more specific products (such as audioPlayer, MoviePlayer, etc).
    ProductionController
    Controller class to control results of actions being done such as a with a button click.
    Screen
    Class Screen explains the features and specifications of the screen of the product entered.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ItemType
    ItemType enum sets predefined values for audio, visual, audio mobile, and visual mobile.
    MonitorType
    Monitor type enum exists to set the values as a predefined LED or LCD.
